query:
SELECT 
  o.customerId,
  CASE WHEN u.id IS NOT NULL THEN 'EXISTS' ELSE 'MISSING' END as userStatus,
  u.name as userName
FROM (SELECT DISTINCT customerId FROM orders) o
LEFT JOIN users u ON o.customerId = u.id
ORDER BY o.customerId;
